# Архитектура (кратко)

Полная спецификация: `ARCHITECTURE.md`.

## Стек
Vue SPA (`frontend/`) <-> Go API (`backend/`) <-> PostgreSQL

## Frontend
`views/` -> `components/<domain>/` -> `composables/` -> `api/` -> Go

Env: `VITE_API_BASE_URL`

## Backend (Go)
```
cmd/server/main.go
internal/handler -> service -> repository -> PostgreSQL
migrations/*.sql
```

Env: `DATABASE_URL`, `HTTP_ADDR`, `CORS_ORIGINS`
